- A house.

105
00:15:30,972 --> 00:15:33,640
- Alone?
- With my parents.

106
00:15:34,142 --> 00:15:35,434
Siblings?

107
00:15:36,644 --> 00:15:39,229
Well, my sister is going to live
in the backyard

108
00:15:39,314 --> 00:15:41,732
