117
00:16:07,675 --> 00:16:08,717
Yes.

118
00:16:09,844 --> 00:16:12,387
"Lee Holloway."

119
00:16:23,858 --> 00:16:26,068
Could you get me
a cup of coffee with sugar?

120
00:16:55,264 --> 00:16:56,515
(RATTLING)

121
00:17:13,574 --> 00:17:14,574
(PANTING)

122
00:17:27,755 --> 00:17:30,048
