171
00:22:06,033 --> 00:22:07,367
Oh, um...

172
00:22:23,551 --> 00:22:25,593
Okay.

173
00:22:27,138 --> 00:22:31,516
Up at the sides. Wide-eyed.

174
00:22:53,956 --> 00:22:54,956
(LEE CLEARS THROAT)

175
00:22:56,417 --> 00:22:58,209
I brought you these.

176
00:23:05,760 --> 00:23:10,680
