192
00:25:17,725 --> 00:25:19,517
And put out one more.

193
00:25:47,046 --> 00:25:50,089
Mice like to go behind the chairs, too, Lee.

194
00:25:50,633 --> 00:25:52,342
Just because it's hard to reach

195
00:25:52,426 --> 00:25:55,261
