take care of every possibility.

196
00:26:01,602 --> 00:26:03,436
Here. Give me that.

197
00:26:19,370 --> 00:26:20,620
Thank you.

198
00:26:42,559 --> 00:26:43,559
(PHONE RINGING)

199
00:27:03,122 --> 00:27:05,790
