GREY: (SOFTLY) Ms. Holloway.

217
00:28:19,073 --> 00:28:20,365
Mr. Grey?

218
00:28:22,409 --> 00:28:23,910
GREY: I'm not here.

219
00:28:28,332 --> 00:28:29,499
Okay.

220
00:28:36,382 --> 00:28:37,799
I'm afraid he's gone.

221
00:28:38,884 --> 00:28:40,218
